stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft : Creator enters request
    Draft --> Approved : Normal API submit / auto-approve
    Draft --> PendingApproval : Manual queue (database status pending)
    PendingApproval --> Approved : Admin approves
    PendingApproval --> Returned : Admin returns with remarks
    PendingApproval --> Rejected : Admin rejects with remarks
    Returned --> PendingApproval : Creator corrects and resubmits (database status pending)
    Approved --> Inside : Guard logs event-device entry
    Inside --> Outside : Guard logs event-device exit
    Outside --> Inside : Re-entry during active dates
    Inside --> Reconciled : Manual closeout
    Outside --> Reconciled : Event closeout
    Reconciled --> [*]
